			description: [
				"&5Occultism&r is a mod about &6rituals and spirits&r, surrounding the &5Otherworld&r, a realm of demons."
				""
				"This quest chapter will help you get started with the mod."
				""
				"Start by getting your hands on a &5Dictionary of Spirits&r - you can get &5Demon's Dream Seeds&r from breaking grass. One can also be found in your &6Eccentric Tome&r."
