			description: [
				"By planting and growing some &5Demon's Dream Seeds&r, you'll get its fruit."
				""
				"While eating it does &6give you Hunger&r, it also has a chance to &6give you its special effect&r, allowing you to &6see and interact with&r &5Otherworld&r &6materials&r such as &5trees and stone&r."
				""
				"Of note, you might want to eat these &6outside the Phase I world generation&r &7(beyond 5000 blocks away from spawn)&r, or else you'll find nothing."
				""
				"Without the effects of the Fruit, these Otherworld materials will simply take the shape of and behave exactly like placed &6Oak Trees and Andesite&r."
			]
